Class Hall

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Eatery>

    public class Hall
extends Eatery
    This class is an Dining Hall, an instance representation of an All You Care to Eat dining hall on Cornell Campus. A master list of these is created and stored in the MasterEateryList class, and can be used by the main program to access information about Halls This class extends Eatery - see Eatery class for more info
    Author:
    James Stoyell
